{"tid":1246113,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄的公開信，想對青年和學生表達什麼？","createTime":"2019-06-20T14:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T15:37:30.000Z","uid":266121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"19723408d4d7b3c1158d3d73c88a054a0ac5ebb5","tid":1246113,"uid":266121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:42:34.000Z","msg":"香港青年或者學生的悲哀之處在於，一眾高官把自己的子女送國外或者國際學校讀書，卻教育其他的青年與學生要同坐一條船，不知道怎樣同坐？當6.9、6.12、6.16大批青年及學生在街上頂著熱浪，宣示著卑微的要求，冒著催淚彈、布袋彈、橡膠子彈的摧殘的時候，我們沒有看到教育局長楊潤雄發出一點人性的聲音。青年及學生上街，用胡適的話來說，就是你們這幫荒唐的老人家鬧下亂子，要讓學生來承擔、要讓他們拋棄學業、荒廢光陰，來干涉糾正。<br />\n<br />\n請問楊局長，當你在寫這封公開信時，你知道什麼叫「不要臉麼」？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/mount-davis/%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E6%83%B3%E5%B0%8D%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%92%8C%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%94%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC-6785420bd5c9?source=friends_link&amp;sk=8afc7cfafdea58c2825838ec5a143a2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fmount-davis%2F%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%25A4%25E9%259B%2584%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2581%2594%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC-6785420bd5c9%3Fsource%3Dfriends_link%26sk%3D8afc7cfafdea58c2825838ec5a143a2f&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=e0b37672\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/mount-davis/%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E6%83%B3%E5%B0%8D%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%92%8C%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%94%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC-6785420bd5c9?source=friends_link&amp;sk=8afc7cfafdea58c2825838ec5a143a2f</a>"},{"pid":"4431cfc59ee9fd344f356869881a88bd795c3a53","tid":1246113,"uid":266121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:37:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港的悲哀就在於教育局局長也是弱智</strong></span></span>"}]}